285
00:21:21,300 --> 00:21:22,300
In denver...

286
00:21:23,100 --> 00:21:24,400
we saw a family.

287
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:28,150
They had been horribly butchered.

288
00:21:28,185 --> 00:21:30,100
Some said it was your people.

289
