Denver, Colorado
Septemper 28, 1864

306
00:23:32,800 --> 00:23:34,100
Come on, boy, drop back.

307
00:23:54,370 --> 00:23:59,300
We have been traveling under a cloud.

308
00:24:00,800 --> 00:24:01,900
The skies...

309
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:07,200
